trans-unit.source: Contains the data sent to a tracking service by the runtime tracking infrastructure when an <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"></xref> is matched.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder data som er sendt til en Sporingstjenesten av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur når en <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"> </xref> samsvarer.

trans-unit.source: It is also used in the return list of the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.ActivityEvents*> property.
trans-unit.target: Den brukes også i return listen over den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.ActivityEvents*>egenskapen.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.ActivityEvents*>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] When the runtime tracking infrastructure matches an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>, it sends an ActivityTrackingRecord to the tracking service over the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> associated with that tracking service.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Når runtime sporing infrastruktur samsvarer med en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>i en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>, sendes en ActivityTrackingRecord til Sporingstjenesten den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>som er forbundet med denne Sporingstjenesten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: The tracking service can perform whatever action is needed on the data in the tracking record.
trans-unit.target: Sporingstjenesten kan utføre hvilken handling på dataene i sporing-oppføringen.

trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>for aktiviteter knyttet til statusen aktivitetshendelse.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.QualifiedName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> of the activity associated with the activity status event.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.QualifiedName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> for aktiviteter knyttet til aktiviteten status for hendelsen.

trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Guid>som identifiserer den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"> </xref> på overordnet aktivitet for aktiviteter knyttet til statusen aktivitetshendelse.</xref:System.Guid>

trans-unit.target: Én av de <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus"> </xref> verdier.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.DateTime> that indicates the date and time of the activity status event associated with the tracking record.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.DateTime>som viser datoen og klokkeslettet for aktivitetshendelse status tilknyttet sporingsposten.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: The relative order in which the activity status event associated with this tracking record occurred in the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Relativ rekkefølgen som aktivitetshendelse statusen som er forbundet med denne oppføring sporing oppstod i arbeidsflytforekomsten.

trans-unit.target: Dette feltet er ikke angitt for en <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the common language runtime (CLR) type of the activity associated with this <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir common language runtime (CLR) typen aktivitet som er knyttet til dette <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: ActivityType is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: ActivityType er angitt av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of the activity for which this <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"></xref> was created.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>til aktiviteten som denne <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"> </xref> ble opprettet.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of annotations associated with the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"></xref> that was matched.
trans-unit.target: Henter samlingen av merknader som er knyttet til den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"> </xref> som passer.

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er angitt av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"></xref> that contains the annotations that are associated with the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"></xref> that corresponds to this tracking record.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"> </xref> som inneholder merknader som er knyttet til den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"> </xref> som tilsvarer denne oppføring for sporing.

trans-unit.source: Gets a list that contains any data extracted from the workflow for the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"></xref> that was matched.
trans-unit.target: Henter en liste som inneholder data som er hentet fra arbeidsflyten for den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"> </xref> som passer.

trans-unit.source: When an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> is matched, the runtime tracking infrastructure can extract data from the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Når en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>samsvarer, kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur kan trekke ut data fra arbeidsflytforekomsten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: The data to be extracted is specified by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Dataene som skal trekkes ut er angitt i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName> can contain two kinds of objects: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> objects specify member data to be extracted from the activity associated with the activity status event; and, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> objects specify member data to be extracted from the root activity of the workflow.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>kan inneholde to typer objekter: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>objekter angi medlemsdata som skal trekkes ut aktiviteten tilknyttet status aktivitetshendelse; og <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>objekter angi medlemsdata som skal trekkes ut aktiviteten roten av arbeidsflyten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract></xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Both of these extract types can also specify annotations to be returned with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Begge disse hente typer kan også angi merknader som skal returneres med utpakkede dataene.

trans-unit.source: The runtime tracking infrastructure encapsulates each piece of extracted data and its associated annotations in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>, and adds this <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> to Body.
trans-unit.target: Kjøring sporing infrastruktur innkapsler hver del av utpakkede data og tilknyttede merknader i en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>, og legger til dette <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>meldingsteksten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er angitt av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: A list of <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"></xref> objects each of which contains a single piece of extracted data and its associated annotations.
trans-unit.target: En liste over <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"> </xref> objekter som inneholder ett enkelt utpakkede data og tilknyttede merknader.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the date and time that the activity status event occurred.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir datoen og klokkeslettet som status aktivitetshendelse oppstod.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.DateTime> is Greenwich Mean Time (UTC).
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.DateTime>er Greenwich Mean Time (UTC).</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: EventDateTime is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: EventDateTime er angitt av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.DateTime> value.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.DateTime>verdi.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates the order in the workflow instance of the activity status event that matched the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir rekkefølgen arbeidsflytforekomsten av status for aktivitetshendelse som samsvarer med den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: EventOrder indicates the relative order of the event that matched the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> within the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: EventOrder angir relativ rekkefølgen av hendelsen som samsvarer med den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>i arbeidsflytforekomsten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: EventOrder is unique within a workflow instance, but it is not guaranteed to be sequential.
trans-unit.target: EventOrder er unikt innenfor en arbeidsflytforekomst, men garanteres ikke være sammenhengende.

trans-unit.source: EventOrder is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: EventOrder er angitt av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: A value that indicates the order of the activity status event in the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: En verdi som angir rekkefølgen av status for aktivitetshendelse i arbeidsflytforekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the execution status of the activity associated with this <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir kjøring av status for aktiviteten tilknyttet denne <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A workflow instance only emits activity status events when the execution status of an activity instance changes.
trans-unit.target: En arbeidsflytforekomst avgir bare aktiviteten Statushendelser når kjøringsstatusen for en Aktivitetsforekomst endres.

trans-unit.source: Therefore an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> can only be matched when an activity execution status change occurs.
trans-unit.target: Derfor en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>bare samsvarer når det oppstår en statusendring for aktiviteten kjøring.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: ExecutionStatus contains the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus?displayProperty=fullName> that triggered the match and caused the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> to be sent.
trans-unit.target: ExecutionStatus inneholder den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus?displayProperty=fullName>som utløses resultatet og forårsaket av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>sendes.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: It reflects the current status of the activity instance.
trans-unit.target: Den gjenspeiler gjeldende status for Aktivitetsforekomst.

trans-unit.source: ExecutionStatus is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: ExecutionStatus er angitt av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Én av de <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus"> </xref> verdier.

trans-unit.source: Context of the parent activity.
trans-unit.target: Konteksten til den overordnede aktiviteten.

trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Guid>som identifiserer den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"> </xref> for aktiviteter knyttet til aktiviteten status for hendelsen.</xref:System.Guid>
